action_item_prompt:
Extract all actionable tasks from the following email. For each task identify: the specific action required, any deadline mentioned, and priority level.

Email Content:
From: {sender}
Subject: {subject}
Body: {body}

Respond in JSON format:
{
  "tasks": [
    {
      "task": "description",
      "deadline": "deadline or 'Not specified'",
      "priority": "High/Medium/Low"
    }
  ]
}

If no action items, return: {"tasks": []}

summary_prompt:
Provide a concise summary of the following email in 2-3 sentences. Focus on the main purpose and any action items.

Email Content:
From: {sender}
Subject: {subject}
Body: {body}

